## Personas

Activate a persona by telling Claude: _"Act as the [persona name] persona."_

| Intent | Persona | Activate with |
|--------|---------|---------------|
| Code, architecture, debugging | Developer | `Act as the Developer persona` |
| Requirements, user stories, docs | Product Manager | `Act as the Product Manager persona` |
| Tests, security audit, QA | Quality Engineer | `Act as the Quality Engineer persona` |
| CI/CD, pipelines, observability | DevOps Engineer | `Act as the DevOps Engineer persona` |
| Cloud infra, IaC, networking | Cloud Engineer | `Act as the Cloud Engineer persona` |
| Data analysis, ML, experiments | Data Scientist | `Act as the Data Scientist persona` |
| Delivery planning, milestones | Project Manager | `Act as the Project Manager persona` |

Default (no persona stated): **Developer**.

